# A dependency unit's CLASS METHOD calls an io native (io.stat). Method bodies
# emit after the io runtime, so their io/os needs must be pre-scanned across ALL
# units, not just main -- else the dep's z_io_stat is called but never declared
# (implicit decl / invalid init). Mirrors zvfs FSProvider/ZVfs.registerFS calling
# io.stat when compiling zparser.
main: function is {
    pr: xunit_io_method.Prober tag: 0.u32
    b: pr.probe p: "no_such_path_zzqq"
    print "missing=\{b}"
}
